@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Us | EasySystems</PageTitle>

<div class="about-page">

    <section class="about-hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">About EasySystems</p>
        <h1>We help businesses launch online with confidence</h1>
        <p>
            EasySystems builds modern online stores and digital systems for small businesses
            that want a professional online presence without technical stress.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>Who we are</h2>
            <p>
                We are a digital solutions company focused on helping businesses create online stores,
                manage requests, and grow with simple, modern systems.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>What we do</h2>
            <p>
                We design and build e-commerce stores, customer dashboards, admin systems,
                automated emails, and structured project request flows.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>Why we exist</h2>
            <p>
                Many small businesses want to sell online but do not know where to start.
                EasySystems makes the process clear, organized, and professional.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-values">
        <div>
            <span>01</span>
            <h3>Clear Process</h3>
            <p>Customers know exactly what happens after they send a request.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <span>02</span>
            <h3>Professional Design</h3>
            <p>Every store is built to look modern, trustworthy, and easy to use.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <span>03</span>
            <h3>Business Focus</h3>
            <p>We build solutions that help businesses save time and grow online.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</div>